{"tid":2328314,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"［港漫］ 我和殭屍有個約會討論區","createTime":"2020-12-16T12:54:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T17:31:32.000Z","uid":325346,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8a03c5e4c2ffc309b14098e5375e07c2fe18005c","tid":2328314,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T12:54:43.000Z","msg":"轉眼間序章聽日就出最後一期<br />\n主角會係山本一夫<br />\n<br />\n好少睇港漫，只係睇過幾期古惑仔同脫北者咁<br />\n估唔到港漫可以咁精彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬小玲好撚索<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以一J<br />\n<br />\n小玲正過珍珍<br />\n<br />\n粉毛玲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋珍珍小玲的情感好sheshe feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小玲為左保護珍珍作出犧牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />偉大<br />\n<br />\n漫畫同電視劇有分別，好似另一個平行時空<br />\n<br />\nBtw,2021年殭屍重啟<br />\n<br />\n個post長期討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nEnjoy <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rgXNZTa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrgXNZTa.jpg&h=0ebfa7f3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wucm4ka.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwucm4ka.jpg&h=1a249a13&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/28ff8M8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F28ff8M8.jpg&h=3fa3f144&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7d8c0a4d88e715ad38632b9f9cacba5a73ba77b","tid":2328314,"uid":22633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T12:58:00.000Z","msg":"鄭建和啲港漫可以買黎睇下，<br />\n冇古惑仔，龍虎門果啲咁老土架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":